Package colorguard

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • colorguard.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Flag, Piece, Powerup

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    GameObject serves as the superclass for all objects in the game (Pieces and Powerups). GameObject defines a location, but its type is not yet defined.
    Author:
    atripathi499
